title Dynamic View: Task Management\nLuồng đăng ký tài khoản User

actor <<Person>>\nUser as User
participant <<Container>>\nUI as UI
participant <<Container>>\nAPI Gateway as API Gateway
participant <<Container>>\nAuthentication Service as Authentication Service
participant <<Container>>\nAuthentication DB as Authentication DB
participant <<Container>>\nMessage Broker as Message Broker
participant <<Container>>\nProfile Service as Profile Service
participant <<Container>>\nProfile DB as Profile DB
participant <<Container>>\nTask Service as Task Service
participant <<Container>>\nTask DB as Task DB

User->UI: 1. Submit form
UI->API Gateway: 2. POST /api/auth/register
API Gateway->Authentication Service: 3. Forward request
Authentication Service->Authentication DB: 4. Lưu thông tin User mới
Authentication Service->Message Broker: 5. Publish 'user.created' event
Profile Service->Message Broker: 6. Subscribe 'user.created' event
Profile Service->Profile DB: 7. Tạo default Profile
Task Service->Message Broker: 8. Subscribe 'user.created' event
Task Service->Task DB: 9. Tạo default Workspace
